{"tid":1285420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王晶上內地節目狠批周星馳：拍戲只為錢！ 主持:跟你一樣嗎?","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:21:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5676c32439fe917e277b2569c46c5df1df76e77d","tid":1285420,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時，王晶與周星馳的組合是無厘頭喜劇和高票房的象徵！只可惜，二人積怨後，沒了周星馳的王晶作品早已風光不再，反而集編導演於一身的周星馳輝煌依舊。日前，王晶在內地清談節目《圓桌派》中承認周星馳是最好的喜劇演員，更講道：「我估計後面三十年都很難有人追到他。」，但就公開批評周星馳從未為過香港人拍戲，只為錢，而引起不少網民討論！<br />\n<br />\n在內地清談節目《圓桌派》中，王晶被主持人梁文道問道：「（像周星馳的電影，那個時候他是為香港人拍&hellip;&hellip;）他從來不會為香港人拍。（就一開始吧，是嗎？）他為錢拍而已。」另一主持人竇文濤聞言就笑言：「像你一樣嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2992829/org/ff510c83d928112e034019c0ac3eb988.jpg/_1XrnQYnlfKgCifOPVXIZ4TmDDft0wRGSnWqOkp1qjo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2992829%2Forg%2Fff510c83d928112e034019c0ac3eb988.jpg%2F_1XrnQYnlfKgCifOPVXIZ4TmDDft0wRGSnWqOkp1qjo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=32938f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2992851/org/2ffe71d7a76395759eef2b45582020b4.jpg/0UFYSd3JdJiGDKR9p5N2uHiEC-nxYl3aFNfLAhTXywI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2992851%2Forg%2F2ffe71d7a76395759eef2b45582020b4.jpg%2F0UFYSd3JdJiGDKR9p5N2uHiEC-nxYl3aFNfLAhTXywI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0700ea3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1168f2e6052e539f960b0881a3e4b27f27857ce3","tid":1285420,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FZPNW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FZPNW0.png&h=462f3b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDsYGg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDsYGg0.jpg&h=7ae1e84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vM0jqJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvM0jqJ6.jpg&h=0a757883&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dce023999089f34ec79b29662ee9388bfce1e1e4","tid":1285420,"uid":3206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae899edcfcbd8d0171212b828ef4fb610d6013c3","tid":1285420,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e337e52c049b558beacda3a00ca586eeb3ea9809","tid":1285420,"uid":56323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"另一主持人竇文濤聞言就笑言：「像你一樣嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n垃圾話人垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ad76cc8420356977dd4789ef147549f07f62fd","tid":1285420,"uid":264790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"以前在鑽石山附近番學，<br />\n成日都喺荷廣KFC見到呢個肥佬。<br />\n佢一個人食一桶雞，成個人都油淋淋，勁核突。"},{"pid":"cbf720f83e80b1182218b4f5adf56522e5dd9e8d","tid":1285420,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f36edea67ece93f5ee1c6d6403f2465e596ffeb","tid":1285420,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"叫王晶個囡出黎拍王大導最鐘意嘅三級片"}]}